      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must have documented verification test suite and version-controlled release process consistent with MRL 2 requirements.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022 R2 is used under an institutional SQA plan that includes regression testing, version control via Git, and documented release notes. All solver unit tests pass. SQA level is consistent with MRL 2 expectations for a Class II device submission."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
