      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric must be defined and applied between simulation output and experimental measurement for each operating point.",
      "rationale": "NIH predicted vs. measured comparison performed at all five operating points using percent difference metric. Maximum deviation is 18% at the 6 LPM / 3500 RPM condition, within the pre-specified 20% acceptance band. Trend across operating points is correctly captured by the model."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the quantities of interest",
