      "rationale": "Validation experiments use the same FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry as the COU model. Operating conditions span the clinical CPB range (4–6 LPM, 2500–4000 RPM). Blood analog properties match clinical hematocrit range. Validation scenario is judged sufficiently representative of the COU for MRL 2 credibility."
