    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed per MRL 2 scoping, consistent with ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4 requirements for a Class II device with medium model influence and high decision consequence. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions within the COU envelope. RH < 1 criterion is met at all five operating points. Submission is accepted for regulatory decision support.",
